{\plain \fs24 \f1 \tab Infant and maternal mortality are tragically high, but 
infant welfare work without birth control is making matters \softline
worse, for it saves the infants, only to let them starve later \softline
on.  As in other countries, welfare work without birth control is \softline
dysgenic and chaotic, cruel as well as planless.\par
}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \tab I have attended many meetings of women in my lifetime, but \softline
the All India Woman{\u8217\'92}s Conference will remain one of the \softline
outstanding inspirations of my life.  I found among these women \softline
an outspoken directness of opinion, a fearlessness in facing \softline
issues as they are, that we in America would do well to follow.  \softline
The Conference passed a resolution in favor of establishing birth \softline
control clinics.\par
